text: Ly Chan Siha is a Cambodian actress. She starred in the movies Gratefulness (2003) and Moronak Meada (2004). She won the award for Best Actress for playing the title role in Moronak Meada. == References == Category:Cambodian film actresses Category:Living people Category:21st-century Cambodian actresses Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
